<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Dwarf Discardation Deck of Doom</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Big Yoda</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">A no rare deck that discards many, many cards from your opponents using Dwarves and Uruk-Hai. Should be able to do enough damage to slow your opponent and make it a nice long game.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Starting<br>
